status-quo.name: Status Quo
status-quo.description: Continue with current vendor distribution across all 25 vendors

tri-vendor.name: Tri-Vendor Consolidation
tri-vendor.description: Consolidate to top 3 vendors: STRYKER, ZIMMER BIOMET, JOHNSON & JOHNSON. Represents 85.3% of current spend.

dual-premium.name: Dual Premium Strategy
dual-premium.description: Focus on top 2 premium vendors: STRYKER, ZIMMER BIOMET. Maximum standardization with proven quality.

dual-value.name: Dual Value Strategy
dual-value.description: Balance premium quality (Stryker) with value pricing (Smith & Nephew) for cost optimization.

single-vendor.name: Single Vendor Strategy
single-vendor.description: Maximum consolidation to STRYKER only. Highest savings potential but significant surgeon disruption.
